      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ABOVE THEM ALL (3) has been in the minors the last two, the latest showing blistering pace early but gathered in and finished a 1.3 lengths second over 515m this track in 29.41. Although beaten ran one of the quickest times on the card last start. Rates highly and will give a great sight. FLYING CURRENCY (4) was in the placings last time but shapes well for this on her strong win the start prior, getting around this track over 515m in 29.55. Must include on winning run two back. OBSCURUS (2) recorded a 4 length third in a Grade 5 last time 29.69 at this track and trip and also jumping from the same draw. Has the ability and looks a key chance. OKLAHOMA BALE (8) is worth including after a top-three finish at big odds most recently.",
